{"tid":2198042,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[體育政治化] NFL覺醒 今季開波前唱埋黑人國歌","createTime":"2020-09-11T05:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T17:10:21.000Z","uid":311819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44e33df376d5d5fa4a5e7a22b2bf18736e6402a0","tid":2198042,"uid":311819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"美國橄欖球聯盟(NFL)今季球賽美國時間星期四晚開波 <br />\n除咗開波之前一向都有嘅唱國歌環節之餘 NFL為咗發聲響應種族歧視今日喺播國歌廿分鐘之前由黑人女歌手Alicia Keys獻唱黑人國歌 &quot;Lift Every Voice and Sing&quot;<br />\n<br />\n德州人全隊就決定兩首歌都唔出場匿埋起更衣室 酋長全隊就手翹手唱晒兩首歌<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.breitbart.com/media/2020/09/Getty-Images_Jamie-Squire-2-640x480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.breitbart.com%2Fmedia%2F2020%2F09%2FGetty-Images_Jamie-Squire-2-640x480.jpg&h=98e40aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩邊 end zone 分別寫咗 需要我哋一齊 同埋 結束種族主義<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ehl5iQlX0AsBikU?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEhl5iQlX0AsBikU%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=a38d1e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EhlkjI_UwAAMUrI?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEhlkjI_UwAAMUrI%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=0d98b83a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賽後結果係酋長34分贏20分德州人<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.breitbart.com/sports/2020/09/10/texans-leave-field-chiefs-stand-arm-in-arm-for-national-anthem-black-national-anthem/?fbclid=IwAR09QUG3tR8RJGxye722ezCpXcwCshXnWNdU_4VriBEQODKC81WwfpxTlos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.breitbart.com%2Fsports%2F2020%2F09%2F10%2Ftexans-leave-field-chiefs-stand-arm-in-arm-for-national-anthem-black-national-anthem%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR09QUG3tR8RJGxye722ezCpXcwCshXnWNdU_4VriBEQODKC81WwfpxTlos&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=2fbb56fc\" target=\"_blank\">